t/uploads/2024/10/Sweaty-Ceilings-book-cover.-Credit-PRESS-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sweaty-Ceilings-book-cover.-Credit-PRESS-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sweaty-Ceilings-book-cover.-Credit-PRESS-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sweaty-Ceilings-book-cover.-Credit-PRESS-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sweaty-Ceilings-book-cover.-Credit-PRESS-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>发行的一本庆祝伦敦独立音乐场所的书籍众筹是出版<em>出汗的天花板</em>。</p><p>这本书是对城市基层音乐场所的庆祝活动，例如风车，100俱乐部，回报室，飞蛾俱乐部，科科，Seabright Arms，Cafe Oto，Cafe Oto，Shacklewell Arms等。</p><p>在跨学科艺术家和设计师索菲·莫（Sophie Mo）和音乐经理塔什·卡茨（Tash Cutts）的带领下， <em style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;">出汗的天花板</em>将在30个地标地点的幕后花费大会，展示了作家，音乐家和文化雕像的访谈和故事，所有这些人都阐明了该场所历史的历史的灯光和文化重要性。它还将在关闭的场地上包含一个其他聚光灯功能。 </p><figure id="attachment_3799120" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3799120" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3799120" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sweaty-Ceilings-book-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="“出汗天花板”的书籍海报。信用：出版" width="2000" height="1050" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sweaty-Ceilings-book-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sweaty-Ceilings-book-poster.-Credit-PRESS-400x210.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sweaty-Ceilings-book-poster.-Credit-PRESS-800x420.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sweaty-Ceilings-book-poster.-Credit-PRESS-696x365.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sweaty-Ceilings-book-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1392x731.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sweaty-Ceilings-book-poster.-Cred